    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Summoning Spell</strong> </p><p>You conjure one &amp;reference[elemental]{elemental} of challenge rating 4 or lower.*</p><ul><li><p>The elemental is friendly to you and your companions and follows your instructions.</p></li><li>The elemental acts after your turn in initiative.</li></ul><ul><li>If you don't issue any commands, the elemental only defends itself from attackers and otherwise does nothing.</li><li>When the spell ends, the elemental doesn't disappear. Instead, it gains free will, often in a way that makes it hostile to its summoner.</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> The challenge rating of the summoned creature increases by 1 for every spell level above 4th.</p>",
            "chat": ""
        },
